query:
INSERT INTO market_order (
    id,
    item_unique_name,
    location_id,
    quality_level,
    enchantment_level,
    unit_price_silver,
    amount,
    auction_type,
    expires_at,
    created_at,
    updated_at)
SELECT DISTINCT ON (id)
    id,
    item_unique_name,
    location_id,
    quality_level,
    enchantment_level,
    unit_price_silver,
    amount,
    auction_type,
    expires_at,
    created_at,
    updated_at
FROM UNNEST(
    $1::BIGINT[],
    $2::VARCHAR[],
    $3::VARCHAR[],
    $4::INT[],
    $5::INT[],
    $6::INT[],
    $7::INT[],
    $8::VARCHAR[],
    $9::TIMESTAMP[],
    $10::TIMESTAMP[],
    $11::TIMESTAMP[]) 
    AS market_order(
        id,
        item_unique_name,
        location_id,
        quality_level,
        enchantment_level,
        unit_price_silver,
        amount,
        auction_type,
        expires_at,
        created_at,
        updated_at)
ON CONFLICT (id) DO
    UPDATE SET
        unit_price_silver = EXCLUDED.unit_price_silver,
        amount = EXCLUDED.amount,
        expires_at = EXCLUDED.expires_at,
        updated_at = EXCLUDED.updated_at
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1 FROM market_order WHERE id = EXCLUDED.id
)
